title: HIgh Platinum/Low Diamond Streamer! Mid Main!
body:
Hey guys,

I am starting out streaming and would love for you to come join me! I am placed currently around the High Platinum/Low diamond andI main mid lane, mostly Annie and Ahri at the moment but I also play a lot of Katarina (If she isnt banned).

I will be doing giveaways of RP and Steam credit in the future if all goes well!

But yeah, come join me over on twitch and have a yarn or ask a few questions @ http://www.twitch.tv/cookiezznz
